%% Diagram: Delivery receipts and async status flow
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Channel processor
    participant Pv as Provider (APNs/FCM/SES/Twilio)
    participant Dev as End device / inbox
    participant CB as Callback ingestor (webhook/SNS)
    participant DS as delivery_status (Cassandra)
    participant TR as Tracing pipeline

    CP->>Pv: Send notification (HTTP/2 / API / SMTP)
    Pv-->>CP: Sync ack: provider_id or 4xx/5xx
    CP->>DS: status=sent OR failed, provider_id, attempt
    CP->>TR: span: provider-ack

    alt Failure (retryable)
        CP->>CP: schedule retry (exp. backoff + jitter)
    else Failure (terminal: invalid token)
        CP->>DS: status=failed, error_code
        CP->>CP: mark token invalid
    end

    Pv-)Dev: Deliver / open / click / bounce
    Dev-)Pv: User interaction (open / click)
    Pv-)CB: Async receipt event (BigQuery / SNS / status webhook)
    CB->>DS: status=delivered/opened/clicked/bounced, timestamp
    CB->>TR: span link to notification trace
